	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In the last week I've become obsessed with implementing an NES on an FPGA from the ground up.  The 6502 core is coming along nicely.
<br />
<br />I've been documenting the progress at <a href="http://www.konkers.net/blog/topics/electronics/knes/" class="postlink">http://www.konkers.net/blog/topics/electronics/knes/</a> for those who are interested.
<br />
<br />Cheers,
<br />    konkers

		

