	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Can't speak for others but I don't have one. My goal is to interface with original hardware and do so with as few gates as possible. So far I have most of a low-level PPU, composite video generator and a CPU without the PLA/instruction decoder. I haven't worked on it in nearly a year (too frustrating on a netbook) so there won't be any progress from me for a while. I understand some guys besides Kevtris do have games playable though.

		

